rg/resource/Eucharist\", \"score\": 0.9999999991650839, \"rank\": 8.346733427235958e-10, \"text\": \"Eucharist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\"}, {\"begin\": 4743, \"end\": 4747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"score\": 0.9946560364499772, \"rank\": 0.005372667911965067, \"text\": \"Mass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his July 27 statement\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"Cozzens\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4523}, {\"ngram\": \"the irony\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4544}, {\"ngram\": \"tens of thousands\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4582}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4654}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4668}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"live telecast\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"the public mockery\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Da Vinci's Last Supper, he said, \\\"was depicted in heinous fashion, leaving us in such shock, sorry and righteous anger that words cannot describe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4751, \"end\": 4759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.465439435519753e-35, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heinous fashion\", \"from\": 4801, \"to\": 4816}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4828}, {\"ngram\": \"such shock\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 4842}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 4864, \"to\": 4869}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cozzens urged Christians, and Catholics in particular, to respond with prayer and fasting, saying, \\\"We are invited to enter into this moment of passion with him, this moment of public shame, mockery, and persecution.\\\"\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 5120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4917, \"end\": 4927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9921992567180183, \"rank\": 0.006643844996118731, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4933, \"end\": 4942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.274628221588256e-20, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cozzens\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4910}, {\"ngram\": \"prayer\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 4980}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5043}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"public shame\", \"from\": 5080, \"to\": 5092}, {\"ngram\": \"mockery\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"persecution\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do this through prayer and fasting,\\\" he said, urging Catholics to pray at Sunday Mass for \\\"healing and forgiveness for all those who participated in this mockery.\\\"\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5179, \"end\": 5188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.274628221588256e-20, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prayer\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5148}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday Mass\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5211}, {\"ngram\": \"healing\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5224}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 5229, \"to\": 5240}, {\"ngram\": \"this mockery\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For those who speak publicly about the performance, Cozzens urged Christians to speak clearly, but with charity.\", \"from\": 5291, \"to\": 5403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5357, \"end\": 5367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9921992567180183, \"rank\": 0.006643844996118731, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5341}, {\"ngram\": \"Cozzens\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5350}, {\"ngram\": \"charity\", \"from\": 5395, \"to\": 5402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bishop Robert Barron of Winona-Rochester, Minnesota, founder of the popular Word on Fire ministry which is a benefactor ofCrux, joined the chorus.\", \"from\": 5405, \"to\": 5551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5412, \"end\": 5425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.613180401256583e-34, \"text\": \"Robert Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\"}, {\"begin\": 5429, \"end\": 5445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Catholic_Diocese_of_Winona\\u2013Rochester\", \"score\": 0.9892654137746267, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winona-Rochester\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Catholic_Diocese_of_Winona\\u2013Rochester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Catholic_Diocese_of_Winona\\u2013Rochester\"}, {\"begin\": 5447, \"end\": 5456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.999997990230641, \"rank\": 2.009768312307817e-06, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"the popular Word\", \"from\": 5469, \"to\": 5485}, {\"ngram\": \"Fire ministry\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5502}, {\"ngram\": \"a benefactor\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5524}, {\"ngram\": \"the chorus\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a video post on X, Barron said the parody reflected a \\\"deeply secularist postmodern society\\\" and represented \\\"gross mockery.\\\"\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5575, \"end\": 5581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.0666410163183194e-13, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video post\", \"from\": 5556, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 5572, \"to\": 5573}, {\"ngram\": \"the parody\", \"from\": 5587, \"to\": 5597}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"deeply secularist postmodern society\", \"from\": 5608, \"to\": 5647}, {\"ngram\": \"gross mockery\", \"from\": 5666, \"to\": 5679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron questioned why France, which prides itself on a culture of \\\"honoring the individual and of human rights and freedom\\\" based on the country's Christian roots, chose to \\\"mock the Christian faith.\\\"\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5683, \"end\": 5689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.0666410163183194e-13, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 5705, \"end\": 5711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9796816040502914, \"rank\": 0.018573198923477585, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5830, \"end\": 5839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999158818052085, \"rank\": 8.412527126280514e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 5866, \"end\": 5875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999158818052085, \"rank\": 8.412527126280514e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5745}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual\", \"from\": 5759, \"to\": 5773}, {\"ngram\": \"human rights\", \"from\": 5781, \"to\": 5793}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 5798, \"to\": 5805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He urged Christians and Catholics to not be passive, but to make their \\\"voices heard.\\\"\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5894, \"end\": 5904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9921992567180183, \"rank\": 0.006643844996118731, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 5909, \"end\": 5918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.274628221588256e-20, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their \\\"voices\", \"from\": 5950, \"to\": 5963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jewish commentators and people of other faiths also decried the performance on social media.\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 6065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5973, \"end\": 5979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"score\": 0.9999467580341406, \"rank\": 5.324475036377658e-05, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6003}, {\"ngram\": \"other faiths\", \"from\": 6007, \"to\": 6019}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6048}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 6052, \"to\": 6064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In their statement, the French bishops thanked members of other religious denominations who have reached out in the wake of the opening ceremony to express \\\"their solidarity with us.\\\"\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6091, \"end\": 6097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998226960401994, \"rank\": 0.00017733281995343158, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their statement\", \"from\": 6070, \"to\": 6085}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 6114, \"to\": 6121}, {\"ngram\": \"other religious denominations\", \"from\": 6125, \"to\": 6154}, {\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 6179, \"to\": 6187}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6211}, {\"ngram\": \"their solidarity\", \"from\": 6224, \"to\": 6240}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6246, \"to\": 6248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This morning, we think of all the Christians of all the continents who have been hurt by the excess and provocation of certain scenes,\\\" they said, and voiced hope that \\\"they understand that the Olympic celebration extends far beyond the ideological biases of a few artists.\\\"\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6287, \"end\": 6297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9921992567180183, \"rank\": 0.006643844996118731, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the continents\", \"from\": 6301, \"to\": 6319}, {\"ngram\": \"the excess\", \"from\": 6342, \"to\": 6352}, {\"ngram\": \"provocation\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6368}, {\"ngram\": \"certain scenes\", \"from\": 6372, \"to\": 6386}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6415}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic celebration\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6466}, {\"ngram\": \"the ideological biases\", \"from\": 6486, \"to\": 6508}, {\"ngram\": \"a few artists\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport, the bishops said, \\\"is a wonderful human activity that deeply rejoices the hearts of athletes and spectators.\", \"from\": 6529, \"to\": 6644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 6529, \"to\": 6534}, {\"ngram\": \"the bishops\", \"from\": 6536, \"to\": 6547}, {\"ngram\": \"a wonderful human activity\", \"from\": 6558, \"to\": 6584}, {\"ngram\": \"the hearts\", \"from\": 6606, \"to\": 6616}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6620, \"to\": 6628}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympism is a movement at the service of this reality of unity and human fraternity.\\\"\", \"from\": 6645, \"to\": 6730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 6645, \"to\": 6653}, {\"ngram\": \"a movement\", \"from\": 6657, \"to\": 6667}, {\"ngram\": \"the service\", \"from\": 6671, \"to\": 6682}, {\"ngram\": \"this reality\", \"from\": 6686, \"to\": 6698}, {\"ngram\": \"unity\", \"from\": 6702, \"to\": 6707}, {\"ngram\": \"human fraternity\", \"from\": 6712, \"to\": 6728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us get to the field of competitions, may it bring truth, consolation and joy to all!\\\"\", \"from\": 6732, \"to\": 6822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6737, \"to\": 6739}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 6747, \"to\": 6756}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 6760, \"to\": 6772}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 6787, \"to\": 6792}, {\"ngram\": \"consolation\", \"from\": 6794, \"to\": 6805}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 6810, \"to\": 6813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"they said.\", \"from\": 6823, \"to\": 6833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Elise Ann Allen on X:@eliseannallen Tuesdays on Today's top stories delivered straight into your inbox.\", \"from\": 6835, \"to\": 6947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6852, \"end\": 6857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"score\": 0.9990027029309553, \"rank\": 0.0009628589055718707, \"text\": \"Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"X:@eliseannallen Tuesdays\", \"from\": 6861, \"to\": 6886}, {\"ngram\": \"Today's top stories\", \"from\": 6890, \"to\": 6909}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 6934, \"to\": 6944}]}]}"